-- Mercury Securities Holds 5.3% Stake in Dar Al Arkan, Data Show
-- B y   Z a i n a b   F a t t a h
-- 2012-07-15T10:34:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-15/mercury-securities-holds-5-3-stake-in-dar-al-arkan-data-show.html
Mercury Securities holds the third-
largest stake in  Dar Al Arkan Real Estate Development Co. (ALARKAN) ,  Saudi
Arabia ’s largest property company, with 5.3 percent of shares,
according to data on the website of Saudi Arabia’s stock
exchange. The bourse didn’t provide details about Mercury.  To contact the reporter on this story:
